FunctionLayer.Calculation

Class CarportCalculation

  • java.lang.Object
    • FunctionLayer.Calculation.CarportCalculation

  • public class CarportCalculation
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains methods for calculating every dimension of the total carport solution.
    The calculations are used to generate drawings, bill-of-material and the final quote.
    Author:
    Alexander Pihl, Mick Larsen, Morten Rahbek, Per Kringelbach, Jean-Poul Leth-MÃ¸ller

        ROOF_TRAPEZ_LENGTH - Length of a roof trapez plate (Assumed value from FOG website)
        ROOF_TRAPEZ_WIDTH - Width of a roof trapez plate (Assumed value from FOG website)
        customerRoofAngle - The customer selected roof angle
